s/Web/API/WEBGL_depth_texture\"><code>WEBGL_depth_texture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WEBGL_draw_buffers\"><code>WEBGL_draw_buffers</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WEBGL_lose_context\"><code>WEBGL_lose_context</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext\"><code>WebGL2RenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLActiveInfo\"><code>WebGLActiveInfo</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLBuffer\"><code>WebGLBuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLContextEvent\"><code>WebGLContextEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLFramebuffer\"><code>WebGLFramebuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>WebGLObject</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLProgram\"><code>WebGLProgram</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLQuery\"><code>WebGLQuery</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderbuffer\"><code>WebGLRenderbuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLSampler\"><code>WebGLSampler</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLShader\"><code>WebGLShader</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLShaderPrecisionFormat\"><code>WebGLShaderPrecisionFormat</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLSync\"><code>WebGLSync</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLTexture\"><code>WebGLTexture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLTransformFeedback\"><code>WebGLTransformFeedback</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLUniformLocation\"><code>WebGLUniformLocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLVertexArrayObject\"><code>WebGLVertexArrayObject</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API\">WebGL API</a> の <strong><code>WebGLRenderingContext.bindBuffer()</code></strong> メソッドは、与えられた <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLBuffer\"><code>WebGLBuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> をターゲットに結合します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">void gl.bindBuffer(target, buffer);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"引数","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"target\">target</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>結合する場所 (ターゲット) の <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API/Types\"><code>GLenum</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> です。以下の値を与えることができます。</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li><code>gl.ARRAY_BUFFER</code>: 頂点の属性を含むバッファーで、頂点座標、テクスチャ座標データや、頂点色データのようなものです。</li>\n      <li><code>gl.ELEMENT_ARRAY_BUFFER</code>: 要素の位置指定に使われるバッファーです。</li>\n      <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext\">WebGL 2 context <small>(en-US)</small></a> を使用している場合は、更に以下の値を利用することができます。\n        <ul>\n          <li><code>gl.COPY_READ_BUFFER</code>: バッファーオブジェクトを他へコピーするためのバッファーです。</li>\n          <li><code>gl.COPY_WRITE_BUFFER</code>: バッファーオブジェクトを他へコピーするためのバッファーです。</li>\n          <li><code>gl.TRANSFORM_FEEDBACK_BUFFER</code>: 書き戻し操作を変換するバッファーです。</li>\n          <li><code>gl.UNIFORM_BUFFER</code>: ユニフォームブロックの格納に使われるバッファーです。</li>\n          <li><code>gl.PIXEL_PACK_BUFFER</code>: ピクセル移動操作に使われるバッファーです。</li>\n          <li><code>gl.PIXEL_UNPACK_BUFFER</code>: ピクセル移動操作に使われるバッファーです。</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"buffer\">buffer</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>結合する <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLBuffer\"><code>WebGLBuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> です。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返り値","title":"返り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>ありません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例外","title":"例外","isH3":true,"content":"<p>一つのターゲットにのみ <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLBuffer\"><code>WebGLBuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> を結合できます。バッファーを他のターゲットに結合しようとすると、<code>INVALID_OPERATION</code> エラーをスローして現在のバッファ結合を同じままにします。</p>\n<p><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLBuffer\"><code>WebGLBuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> が <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/deleteBuffer\"><code>deleteBuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> によって削除されるようにマークされると、(再び) 結合できなくなります。そうしようとしても <code>INVALID_OPERATION</code> エラーが生成されて、現在の結合は変更されません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"バッファーをターゲットに結合","title":"バッファーをターゲットに結合","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> gl <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'webgl'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> buffer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> gl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ngl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">bindBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">ARRAY_BUFFER</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"現在結合されているものの取得","title":"現在結合されているものの取得","isH3":true,"content":"<p>現在のバッファー結合を確認するには、<code>ARRAY_BUFFER_BINDING</code> や <code>ELEMENT_ARRAY_BUFFER_BINDING</code> の定数で問い合わせます。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>gl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getParameter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">ARRAY_BUFFER_BINDING</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ngl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getParameter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">ELEMENT_ARRAY_BUFFER_BINDING</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様策定状況","title":"仕様策定状況","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>仕様</th>\n      <th>策定状況</th>\n      <th>コメント</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/registry/webgl/specs/latest/1.0/#5.14.5\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebGL 1.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">bindBuffer の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n      <td>WebGL 初回定義。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/opengles/sdk/docs/man/xhtml/glBindBuffer.xml\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">OpenGL ES 2.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">glBindBuffer の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">標準</span></td>\n      <td>OpenGL ES 2 API (と同様な) マニュアルページ。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/registry/webgl/specs/latest/2.0/#3.7.1\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebGL 2.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">bindBuffer の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-ed\">編集者草案</span></td>\n      <td>WebGL 2 のために定義を更新。以下の新しい <code>target</code> バッファーを追加。 <code>gl.COPY_READ_BUFFER</code>, <code>gl.COPY_WRITE_BUFFER</code>, <code>gl.TRANSFORM_FEEDBACK_BUFFER</code>, <code>gl.UNIFORM_BUFFER</code>, <code>gl.PIXEL_PACK_BUFFER</code>, <code>gl.PIXEL_UNPACK_BUFFER</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/opengles/sdk/docs/man3/html/glBindBuffer.xhtml\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">OpenGL ES 3.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">glBindBuffer の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">標準</span></td>\n      <td>OpenGL ES 3 API (と同様な) マニュアルページ。</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"ブラウザーの対応","isH3":false,"query":"api.WebGLRenderingContext.bindBuffer","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/bindBuffer/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連項目","title":"関連項目","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/createBuffer\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.createBuffer()</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/deleteBuffer\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.deleteBuffer()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/isBuffer\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.isBuffer()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li>他のバッファ: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLFramebuffer\"><code>WebGLFramebuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderbuffer\"><code>WebGLRenderbuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様策定状況","id":"仕様策定状況"},{"text":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"ブラウザーの対応"},{"text":"関連項目","id":"関連項目"}],"summary":"WebGL API の WebGLRenderingContext.bindBuffer() メソッドは、与えられた WebGLBuffer (en-US) をターゲットに結合します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebGLRenderingContext.bindBuffer()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebGLRenderingContext.bindBuffer()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebGLRenderingContext.bindBuffer()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"WebGLRenderingContext.bindBuffer()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/webglrenderingcontext/bindbuffer","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/webglrenderingcontext/bindbuffer/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext","title":"WebGLRenderingContext"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/bindBuffer","title":"WebGLRenderingContext.bindBuffer()"}],"pageTitle":"WebGLRenderingContext.bindBuffer() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}